replies.body:
@Riot, love the game, im trash at it but im addicted and play it regardless.
Love the time and energy you put into updates and game modes and trying to keep things fresh and interesting for all the players.
But if you read all of the comments here from the last few days of people who went to the effort of giving feed back for you, over 90% of them mention URF and want it back. This includes me.
I'm not suggesting force feed it to the masses, because not EVERYONE likes URF, so its not fair. I think what would be fair, is not doubling up on a particular game mode until ALL game modes have gone through the queue. This is the best way to keep things fair and give everyone a chance to play the modes they love.
And will also give the 99% of us a chance to play URF more than twice a year :(

Other than that, thanks for the game I love. Waiting to play the s**t out of URF when its here {{summoner:3}}
